english.segment1: Separate your chief anxieties. Cut the cord, but you won't. Excommunicate from our society. Are you bold? You are not
english.segment2: Oh no. The most terrible, terrible. Archer
english.segment3: You among the league of militants. How little you have learned. Tried and failed to be one of the innocents. Little left of yourself
english.segment4: Little left of myself. Little right of yourself
english.segment5: Oh no. The most terrible, terrible. Archer.
